===Hardware specification=== *CPU: [[Rockchip]] RK3568 @2.0GHz Quad-core ARM (Cortex-A55) *GPU: Mali-G52 (OpenGL ES3.2, OpenCL 2.0); NPU Support 0.8T :VPU (with 4K VP9 and 4K 10-bit H265/H264 decoding) *Storage: 8GB (eMMC 5.1) Flash, TF card (128GB)/MMC card slot *Memory: 2GB (LPDDR4X) SDRAM *Network: 1x 1Gbps, 2x 2.5Gbps Ethernet ports *PCIe: M.2 (Key M), PCIe 2.1 x1, support NVME, PCIe WiFi *USB: 2x USB 3.2 ports *GPIO: 12-pin 0.5mm FPC, 2x 8-pin 1.27mm connectors *Power Source: USB (Type-C) support PD, 5V/9V/12V
